Augustine CAIN v. WINN-DIXIE LOUISIANA, INC. No. 99-C-3037. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Dec. 17, 1999.

Prior report: La.App., — So.2d ——.

In re Cain, Augustine; — Plaintiff; Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review, Parish of Pointe Coupee, 18th Judicial District Court Div. C, Nos. 29,934; to the Court of Appeal, First Circuit, No. 98 CA 0792.

Denied.

CALOGERO, C.J., not on panel. JOHNSON, J., would grant and reinstate the judgment of the trial court.
